@startuml
!include theme.iuml
title 实时视频识别与道路分析时序图
skinparam shadowing false
actor 用户 as User
participant "React 大屏" as Web
participant "FastAPI" as API
participant "CameraHub" as Hub
participant "视觉算法" as Algo
participant "自适应调度器" as Scheduler
participant "RoadLogicService" as Road
database "SQLite/证据库" as DB

User -> Web : 登录、选择摄像头与任务
Web -> API : POST /api/cameras/{id}/start
API -> Hub : start(camera_id)
Hub --> API : VideoStatus
Web -> API : GET 原始/模型 MJPEG
loop 按调度间隔
  API -> Hub : latest_jpeg(camera_id)
  Hub --> API : JPEG
  API -> Scheduler : 任务模式 + 资源 + 最近时延
  Scheduler --> API : 模型/尺寸/阈值/间隔 profile
  API -> Algo : 按 profile 执行车辆监控或道路异常推理
  Algo --> API : AnalysisResult + 标注帧
  API -> Road : enrich(result)
  Road --> API : 道路观测、禁停、拥堵
  API -> DB : 周期保存结果、事件与证据帧
  API --> Web : MJPEG + REST 状态
end
Web --> User : 指标、热力图、事件和历史
@enduml
